name: Tom's Storage 1.21-2.0.0 Fabric
changelog:
2.0.0 Update  
Large parts of the mod was rewritten to improve performance and ease of use  
Placing multiple inventory connectors and connecting them with cable now works without needing an inventory proxy  
Added Inventory Interface for accessing the inventory system  
Added Inventory Configurator:  
- Configures how each inventory is added to the system  
- Allows filtering and priority without needing cable connectors  
- Allows excluding from the inventory system, for multiblock inventories  
- Left click shows all of the connected inventories  
  
Added Filling Cabinet for storing multiple of the same item, but with different components  
  
Currently missing features that will be added later  
- Inventory Proxy  
- Inventory Cable Connectors  
- Remote Inventory System using beacons  
- Localizations are outdated
